3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper formulates the active friending problem as an optimization problem and proposes an algorithm to solve it. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes an algorithm for active friending, which can be seen as a form of intelligent decision-making in social networks.
